Class SCCConsumerStore

  • java.lang.Object
    • explicit.SCCConsumerBitSet
      • explicit.SCCConsumerStore
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SCCConsumer

    public class SCCConsumerStore
extends SCCConsumerBitSet
    SCC consumer that stores lists of the discovered SCCs and BSCCs. The list of BSCCs is computed on demand from the list of SCCs.
